ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, I think this is very helpful in preparing me for TA. I would suggest more problems that would actually happen during TA be discussed in class.

I would strongly recommend this course to another student. The title of the course definitely explains what the course is about: It helps you to get prepared to teach at university by providing tools to improve pronunciation, presentation skills and effective function at university.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The presentations I gave in class have brought me to think what is important in academic teaching, which is obviously very important.

I totally feel more confident to present and explain material related to my field after I have taken this course. I believe I can also use teaching techniques that the instructor has used throughout the term.
